ows a trainer to obliviously publish an encrypted model to a\ncloud provided by a computational resource provider, i.e., without revealing\nthe original model itself to the provider.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Nov 2018 09:18:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-13"}
