 an example of a high-performing thermoelectric\nmaterial where the local atomic structure differs significantly from the\naverage periodic structure observed from Bragg crystallography.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Nov 2018 12:19:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 May 2019 09:08:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-02"}
